# Direct dependencies for RDHPCS Documentation
#
# This file lists the direct dependencies for the project with pinned versions
# to ensure reproducible builds and supply chain security.
#
# To update dependencies:
#   1. Modify the version pins in this file
#   2. Run: pip-compile --generate-hashes requirements.in
#   3. Commit both requirements.in and requirements.txt together
#   4. Changes require review from the security-reviewers team
#
# See CONTRIBUTING.md for detailed instructions on updating dependencies.

